text: Nikos Eleutheriadis (31 August 1937) is a Cypriot footballer. He played in nine matches for the Cyprus national football team from 1960 to 1966. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1937 births Category:Cypriot men's footballers Category:Cyprus men's international footballers Category:Footballers from Nicosia Category:Men's association football goalkeepers Category:AC Omonia players
